project_components

Class FittedCarFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • project_components.Component
      • project_components.FittedComponent
        • project_components.FittedCarFrame

  • public class FittedCarFrame
extends FittedComponent
    It models the carFrame(lateral lift moving guide). It has some sub-Stefano_package.components that defines the structure in a more detailed way than the mere frame.
